{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-component-tsx","path":"/component/PopConfirm/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"5af3113c-2020-57d0-af77-f8c03c3af9fe","excerpt":"简介 用户在使用产品时需要做各种决策，为了减少甚至避免对重要数据的误操作，或对重要操作的误触，我们需要在必要且合适的时候，让用户对操作进行二次确认。 气泡确认框  通常用于中成本的操作的二次确认，其会在点击元素上弹出浮层进行提示确认。防止误操作。 基本构成  图标（A） 文本内容（B） 操作按钮（C） 容器（D…","html":"<!--副标题具体写法见源代码模式-->\n<h2 id=\"简介\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\" aria-label=\"简介 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>简介</h2>\n<p>用户在使用产品时需要做各种决策，为了减少甚至避免对重要数据的误操作，或对重要操作的误触，我们需要在必要且合适的时候，让用户对操作进行二次确认。</p>\n<p>气泡确认框 <code class=\"language-text\">PopConfirm</code> 通常用于中成本的操作的二次确认，其会在点击元素上弹出浮层进行提示确认。防止误操作。</p>\n<h2 id=\"基本构成\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90\" aria-label=\"基本构成 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本构成</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 28.611111111111114%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAGCAYAAADDl76dAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAg0lEQVQY052PUQuCQBCE/f+/rIceIyQiezhMfWiPLtTD3R3RWDC7Xm5hGBg+htkCu1PV1UXkJzdtuf0VqdDgtiOUlzu8f33l/8qShQZfbw6BHJq6wpMCllgkY6GB4d1DJUI5IjwaHA+E09mBPOW/vNi6bGIMA2OME5g5b+HHTWkmVTgD8CnaR6JznNcAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"forms 01\"\n        title=\"forms 01\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/f62b32c9cfc2c26b66c5d1965d2f8b44/dc3b8/forms_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/f62b32c9cfc2c26b66c5d1965d2f8b44/8ef26/forms_01.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/f62b32c9cfc2c26b66c5d1965d2f8b44/c4481/forms_01.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/f62b32c9cfc2c26b66c5d1965d2f8b44/dc3b8/forms_01.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/f62b32c9cfc2c26b66c5d1965d2f8b44/5620d/forms_01.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">图标（A）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">文本内容（B）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">操作按钮（C）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">容器（D）</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>A.图标</strong></p>\n<p>主要用来表示提示的重要程度。U-Design预设部分图标，用户也可以根据自己的需求自定义。</p>\n<p><strong>B.文本内容</strong></p>\n<p>U-Design建议 气泡确认框 <code class=\"language-text\">PopConfirm</code> 的文案公式如下：打断原因+操作带来的后果+用户可以做什么操作。需要注意，整条文案不宜过长。</p>\n<p><strong>C.操作按钮</strong></p>\n<p><strong>D.容器</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"基本样式\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"基本样式 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本样式</h2>\n<h3 id=\"尺寸\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8\" aria-label=\"尺寸 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>尺寸</h3>\n<p><strong>最小宽度</strong></p>\n<p>简洁模式下, U-Design预设了一个边框最小宽度186px。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.055555555555557%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAFCAYAAABFA8wzAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAcklEQVQY052QOQqAQAxFvf/V7K1sbARxzSyJ+7cQx1EGUYuQkPAe5EdKCe5FxK6TGtzctny5hdgotPQBSyWaRoG5B9bpUfZKOEsFowl5YREnC4zp/wkPqbEzREZUNSPNvCjog3AHTrjrGFoL2PrvhjPcAEzkgKpKaXkuAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"styles 01\"\n        title=\"styles 01\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/775564ab60e42f0f68c429c3b3e04eac/dc3b8/styles_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/775564ab60e42f0f68c429c3b3e04eac/8ef26/styles_01.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/775564ab60e42f0f68c429c3b3e04eac/c4481/styles_01.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/775564ab60e42f0f68c429c3b3e04eac/dc3b8/styles_01.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/775564ab60e42f0f68c429c3b3e04eac/5620d/styles_01.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>常用尺寸</strong></p>\n<p>U-Design为气泡确认框<code class=\"language-text\">PopConfirm</code> 设定的文字最大宽度为240px, 超出自动换行显示。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.055555555555557%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"styles 02\"\n        title=\"styles 02\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/fe2a63348603ec810842950d57db9606/dc3b8/styles_02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/fe2a63348603ec810842950d57db9606/8ef26/styles_02.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/fe2a63348603ec810842950d57db9606/c4481/styles_02.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/fe2a63348603ec810842950d57db9606/dc3b8/styles_02.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/fe2a63348603ec810842950d57db9606/5620d/styles_02.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>超长的文本（不建议）</strong></p>\n<p>建议文本最多3行，超出显示滚动条，通过滚动展示全部文本。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.055555555555557%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"styles 03\"\n        title=\"styles 03\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/a7bca5ec3f32f966b31c67a337a02984/dc3b8/styles_03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/a7bca5ec3f32f966b31c67a337a02984/8ef26/styles_03.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/a7bca5ec3f32f966b31c67a337a02984/c4481/styles_03.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/a7bca5ec3f32f966b31c67a337a02984/dc3b8/styles_03.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/a7bca5ec3f32f966b31c67a337a02984/5620d/styles_03.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"设计说明\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\" aria-label=\"设计说明 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设计说明</h2>\n<p>1.气泡确认框没有蒙层，点击确认框以外的区域即可关闭。</p>\n<p>2.用户转化关键节点避免使用二次确认，会中断整个用户购买流程。</p>\n<!--（这部分原来在常见问题部分，移上来了麻烦交互措辞）-->\n<h2 id=\"常见问题\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"常见问题 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>常见问题</h2>\n<h3 id=\"避免滥用\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E6%BB%A5%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"避免滥用 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>避免滥用</h3>\n<p>气泡确认框 <code class=\"language-text\">PopConfirm</code> 是会打断用户操作流的设计，是迫不得已的折中方案：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>其会增加用户操作步骤，降低操作效率；</li>\n<li>打断用户流程，降低转化率；</li>\n<li>影响产品品质，损害用户体验印象。</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"u-md-flex-without-bg\">\n   <div class=\"u-md-mr24\">\n      <p><i class=\"u-md-suggested\"></i>对于中成本的操作，给予提示</p>\n      <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bo